- ✅ **All 5 YAML files** parse as valid YAML (confirmed via `yaml.safe_load`)
- ✅ **All 1 test** passes (`test_all_agent_yamls`)
- ✅ **All sub-recipe paths** referenced in orchestrator exist
- ✅ **All required fields** present in every file (`name`, `version`, `title`, `description`, `instructions`, `settings`)
- ✅ **All versions** bumped to `1.0.1` consistently
- ✅ **No remaining `prompt:` keys** — all standardized to `instructions:`
